title: transfer own data from the official lol server to garena lol server
body: is there a way to do this? transfering the data to garena lol server

replies.body: It's not currently possible to transfer from a Riot supported region to Garena.  Even if we wanted to, I believe they're in entirely different databases that wouldn't allow for a transfer.  Let me know if that clears things up!
alright, thanks for the answer! it's does clears things up
